{"title":"采茶曲","authors":["巴牧"],"dates":[{"year":1959,"month":3,"day":13}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"采茶曲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巴牧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南山忙采茶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"茶树正发芽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山坡换新衣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乐煞万人家。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一群农家女，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"提篮进山洼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来到茶林内，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好似蝶采花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"茶树一行行，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新叶满枝垭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"碧玉从中长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"竹篮装不下。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今年春最早，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春来树开花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"茶林庆丰收，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌声迎彩霞。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}